          <string>Description</string>
          <string>CLR	(1)	MR	Master Reset (Active LOW)		Input
CLK	(2)	CP	Clock (Active HIGH Going Edge)	Input
A-D	(3-6)	P0-P3	Parallel			Inputs
ENP	(7)	CEP	Count Enable Parallel		Input
LOAD	(9)	PE	Parallel Enable (Active LOW)	Input
ENT	(10)	CET	Count Enable Trickle		Input
Q_A-Q_D	(11-14)	Q0-Q3	Parallel Outputs		Outputs
RCO	(15)	TC	Terminal Count 		Output</string>
        </entry>
      </elementAttributes>
